metadata.name: EoV Maiden  #2
metadata.description: Edge of Victory is a thrilling tale of a group of brave maidens who must go to war against evil forces in order to protect their land and their people. But the war is long and grueling, and the maidens must draw on all of their inner strength and courage in order to emerge victorious. Follow the maidens on their epic journey as they fight for justice and for the future of their world.
